        "subject": "LU-3520 build: Modily lbuild to work with mellanox OFED.",
        "message": "LU-3520 build: Modily lbuild to work with mellanox OFED.\n\nThis patch modified lbuild to accept an additional --ofed-filename in\naddition to --ofed-version which permits the building with Mellanox\nofed releases who use the same versioning scheme but a different file\nnaming scheme to OpenFabrics.\n\nSigned-off-by: Ashley Pittman <apittman@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: If5f6f47d29a3872ae41bdf4155ace1b570d6b319\n"
